original: The DayZ Editor is an Open Source 3D Editing tool built to design new areas, create vivid screenshots, and test game mechanics. Users can place any item available in the game, import and export files from all types of mods, and brush the landscape with your new ideas
english: The DayZ Editor is an Open Source 3D Editing tool built to design new areas, create vivid screenshots, and test game mechanics. Users can place any item available in the game, import and export files from all types of mods, and brush the landscape with your new ideas

original: DayZ Editor support is handled through our Discord! Click 'Discord' to join and report bugs / ask questions\nFeedback is always much appreciated!
english: DayZ Editor support is handled through our Discord! Click 'Discord' to join and report bugs / ask questions\nFeedback is always much appreciated!

original: Want to support the DayZ Editor project? Donations are much appreciated, but never required!
english: Want to support the DayZ Editor project? Donations are much appreciated, but never required!
